{"id":543428,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/10/韩东言：白灵在央视《震撼世界的长征》中，到底/","date":"2016-10-26T06:48:27Z","modified":"2016-10-26T06:48:27Z","title":"韩东言：白灵在央视《震撼世界的长征》中，到底做了啥说了啥？","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日，美国华裔艳星白灵在央视纪念长征80周年的纪录片《震撼世界的长征》第六集中出镜一事，引来了大量网民的不满。截至发稿时，中国大陆各大网站及论坛的相关文章均已被删除。《环球时报》在微信公众号和新浪微博发文，不点名批评央视纪录片的《请问！为什么要从美国请一个艳星来“纪念”长征？》（<a href=\"http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:DyoGnuwZs2wJ:weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show%3Fid%3D2309351002474033840967456769+\" target=\"_blank\">谷歌快照</a>）也已被删除。截至发稿时，央视YouTube官方账号所上传的<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0km5W7dIwR4\" target=\"_blank\">第六集</a>已删去白灵出镜部分，央视网官方视频已无法播放，B站<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av6725340/index_6.html\" target=\"_blank\">尚存</a>包含白灵画面的原始视频。</p>\n<p>@韩东言 原微博已被删除（（<a href=\"http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:S8hJVTjh-IYJ:weibo.com/1874361623/EedfYgI1w%3Ftype%3Drepost+\" target=\"_blank\">谷歌快照</a>））。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>@韩东言：</strong><br />\n1、白灵在央视《震撼世界的长征》中，到底做了啥说了啥？<br />\n2、纪录片关于白灵的镜头有六七个，采访有两段不超过30秒。<br />\n3、白灵出现的意义在于美国好莱坞对于中国长征的认识。<br />\n4、白灵出现的原因是美国拍摄的长征，征集志愿者，而白灵报名参加。<br />\n5、建议先看视频再发言，另，价值判断高于道德判断。<br />\n6、不要去否定片子和白灵宣传的长征价值。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92laxeu5oj20zk0qo792.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543429\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92laxeu5oj20zk0qo792.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92laxeu5oj20zk0qo792\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92laxeu5oj20zk0qo792.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92laxeu5oj20zk0qo792-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layere4j20zk0qogob.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543430\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layere4j20zk0qogob.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92layere4j20zk0qogob\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layere4j20zk0qogob.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layere4j20zk0qogob-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layjkjdj20zk0qotbl.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543431\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layjkjdj20zk0qotbl.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92layjkjdj20zk0qotbl\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layjkjdj20zk0qotbl.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92layjkjdj20zk0qotbl-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazdxtyj20zk0qotbg.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543432\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazdxtyj20zk0qotbg.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lazdxtyj20zk0qotbg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazdxtyj20zk0qotbg.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazdxtyj20zk0qotbg-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazuc6ej20zk0qoju2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543433\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazuc6ej20zk0qoju2.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lazuc6ej20zk0qoju2\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazuc6ej20zk0qoju2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lazuc6ej20zk0qoju2-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb0ipoyj20zk0qoq5o.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543434\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb0ipoyj20zk0qoq5o.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lb0ipoyj20zk0qoq5o\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb0ipoyj20zk0qoq5o.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb0ipoyj20zk0qoq5o-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb2htqxj20zk0qon1k.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543435\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb2htqxj20zk0qon1k.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lb2htqxj20zk0qon1k\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb2htqxj20zk0qon1k.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb2htqxj20zk0qon1k-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb18j6kj20zk0qo42f.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543436\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb18j6kj20zk0qo42f.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lb18j6kj20zk0qo42f\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb18j6kj20zk0qo42f.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lb18j6kj20zk0qo42f-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lbcox8xj20zk0qogp8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543437\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lbcox8xj20zk0qogp8.jpg\" alt=\"6fb87d17gw1f92lbcox8xj20zk0qogp8\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lbcox8xj20zk0qogp8.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/6fb87d17gw1f92lbcox8xj20zk0qogp8-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>背景新闻：</strong><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2016/10/161025_china_long_march_backfire\" target=\"_blank\">BBC｜“反华艳星”白灵拍央视长征纪录片　中国网民“暴怒”</a></p>\n<blockquote><p>官方中国中央电视台一套有关中共红军长征80周年的纪录片因起用美籍华人女演员白灵，遭网民与鹰派舆论训斥。</p>\n<p>央视这套《震撼世界的长征》上周在央视军事纪实频道播出白灵参与摄制的一集节目后，《人民日报》旗下《环球时报》在社交媒体刊文，不点名摄制单位起用“污蔑解放军”的“艳星”。</p>\n<p>出生于四川成都的白灵于1990年代移居美国。《环时》文章批评她“在海外走低俗路线”，“自我作贱”。</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18270,18269,9203,10466],"tags":[11813,31906,18804,9149,30319,23589,31905]}